Note 8. Fair V alue Measurements
The Company classifies its fair value measurements of financial instruments into a three-level hierarchy within the Valuation
Hierarchy . Financial instruments are categorized for fair value measurement purposes as recurring or non-r ecurring in nature. There
were no transfers made among the three levels in the V aluation Hierarchy for 2020 and 2019.1 2
