Restricted Stock Units
For RSUs granted on or after March 1, 2020, the awards generally vest ratably over four years.  For RSUs granted befor e March 1,
2020, the awards generally vest after three years . A participant’ s unvested awards are forfeited upon termination of employment. In
the event of termination due to job elimination (as defined by the Company), however , a partici pant will retain a pro-rata portion of
the unvested awards for services performed through the date of termination. In the event a participant terminates employment due to
disability or retirement more than seven months  after receiving the awar d, the participant retains all of their awards without providing
additional service to the Company . Compensation expense is recognized over the shorter of the vesting periods stated in the LTIP or
the date the individual becomes eligible to retire but not less than seven months .
